### What you can bring in

What you can bring in

There are some things you can’t bring into Australia as a traveller. Australia also has strict biosecurity requirements. Be aware of what you can and can’t bring into the country.

### Duty free

Duty free

Most personal items you would carry in your luggage can be brought into Australia tax and duty free. As a traveller you can also buy limited amounts of general goods, alcohol and tobacco duty free.
